== Degmadda Wanlaweyne (Daafeet) == 
----------------------------------------------
Degmada '''Wanlweyne''' (Daafeet) waa degmo ka tirsan degmooyinka Shabeellaha Hoose. Waxaa hostaga tuulooyin fara badan oo garaaya ilaa '''400''' tuulo. Dhaqaalaha dadka degmada ay ku tirsan yihin waxaa ka mida beeraha, iyo xoolaha nool. Degmadan waxaa ku yaala garoonka caalamiga ee BALIDOOGLE Airport. Odayaasha ayaa maamula degmada. 

Degmada w/wayne, beesha '''Hubeer''' wa beesha kaliya ee ugu badan degmadaasi marki lo eego beelaha walaalahoda ee la degan. Degmada wanlaweyn wa xarunta ugu weyn ee beesha Hubeer degto marki lo eego gobolada Baay, Gedo, iyo Jubooyinka, maxa yeelay degmada w/weyn waxa wada degan afarta lafod ee ka koban tahay beesha Hubeer wexeyna degmadasi ku leyihin golle odayal dhaqaamed qadimi ah oo awood leh lona yaqano (Hubeer Hirine) oo marki af maxaga lo fasiro la micno ah Hubeerka mideysan ama isku xiran.
Gollaha odayasha ee Hubeer hirinaha wuxu ka koban yahay afarta lafod ee beesha Hubeer wexeyna isku wada racsan yihin in malaaqa guud ee beesha Hubeer u yahay Malaaq Xusein Axmed Caliyow wuxuna xilka kala waregay maqlaadi hore ee Adan Xusein Malaaq oo hada duqobay kuna nol magalada muqdisho.
Gollaha odayasha ee Hubeer hirinaha daafeet waxa ay fasax siyeen in gobolada alto-jubba in ay doran karan malaaq ayaga u gooni ah madama beeshu ay aad u ballaran tahay, goboladasne ay aad uga fogyihin gobolka sh/hoose oo ah xarunta malaaqa guud ee beesha Hubeer.

Beesha Hubeer, dhaqan ahan malaaq wuxu kaga dhigan yahay abaandulle, oo mar walba u tagan difaaca shacabka, iyo deganada beesha. Hadaba, malaaqa guud ee beesha Hubeer waxa dhaqan ahan lagu caleemo sara guriga yaranka Huliye ee Reereeji gar ahan Lafta Cumaroow qaasatan jufada reer aw ade (aw-cade) oo aad lo qadariyo wane lafta u malaaqa guud u ka amar qato wixi talo iyo tusaale ah. Hadi lacale, malaaqa guud u duqowbo ama howlgab noqdo, waxa uun codsan kara in la bedelo jufada yaranka ah ee reer ade (reer cadde). Haddi lacale lafaha kale ee Hubeer ka koban tahay ay isku qabsadan "Dooro biyoo macabto iyo way cabta" waxa la racaa talada jufada reer aw ade (aw-cadde) oo ah halka ugu dambeyso ee garta lagu qoyo. Dhaqankani ee beesha Hubeer ay ledahay wa dhaqan soojireen ah oo ila 100,000 sano ka hor ay ku dhaqmi jireen.

Degmada w/weyn waxa lagu qiyasay '''1 Milyaan qoys''' oo Hubeer wada ah hadi lagu darro dadka degan tulooyinka fog-fog ee xududaaha laaleh degmooyinka dariska ah.    

